Installation process
====================

    - Copy the root filesystem and initramfs through sftp :    
    ``` bash
        # sftp cdtx@192.168.0.1
        # get developpment/linux/buildroot-2014.02/output/images/bzImage
        # get developpment/linux/buildroot-2014.02/output/images/rootfs.tar
        # get developpment/linux/buildroot-2014.02/board/cdtx/apu/initramfs.cpio.gz
    ```

    - Run installer script
    ``` bash
        # ./install.sh
    ```

